To further investigate the effects of charge recombination dynamics on the efficiencies of the ternary OSCs, we obtained the JSC-light illumination intensity plots for the four devices (Fig. 5a). It is known that JSC has a power-law dependence on the light intensity (Plight), i.e. JSC∝\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
